quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  9,107,"∆Āeen jogitor…ďe juulirde fii lorra, e keefereegu, e senndude hakkunde gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďeen, e tommbaade on kabu…óo Alla e nulaa…óo makko on ko adii. Pellet, he…ďe ngoo…óndira : "min paandaaki si wanaa mo∆ī∆īere" Alla no seedii won de pellet, ko …ďe fenoo…ďe."
  9,108,"Wata a daro (juulugol) e mayre poomaa. Ko juulirde diidiraande kulol Alla gila ka arannde √Īalaande, …ďuri jojjude nde daroto…óaa e mun [juulaa]. Hino e mayre wor…ďe yi…ó…ďe nde …ďe la…ď…ďinotoo. Alla no yi…ói la…ď…ďinotoo…ďe …ďen."
  9,109,"E ko on didir…óo maadi mu'un kulol Alla e welayee makko, …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude, kaa ko on didir…óo maadi mu'un e sera ngasko yirbuka, o yirbida e mayri ka Yiite Jahannama?! Alla feewnataa yim…ďe too√Īoo…ďe …ďen."
  9,110,"Ndin maadi ma…ď…ďe ndi …ďe mahi seerataa ko ndi sikke ka …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe, si wanaa …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen ta∆īay tun. Alla ko ganndu…óo, √Ďee√Īu…óo."
  9,111,"Pellet, Alla sooditirii e goo…óin…ďe …ďen woŇčkiiji ma…ď…ďe …óin, e jaw…óeele ma…ď…ďe …óen won de no woodani …ďe Aljanna. He…ďe ka…ďa fii laawol Alla ngol : he…ďe mbara, he…ďe mbaree. Ko fodoore goonga nde O fodi ka tawreeta, e ka Linjiila e Alqur'aana. Ko hommbo …ďuri Alla huu…ďngol ahdi mun? mbeltoree njeeygu mon ngu njeeeyondir…óon e mum : ko …óuum woni malala mawnungal ngal."